      "content": "Authorization flow: (1) If AUTH_ENABLED=false, all access granted; (2) Validate bearer token, extract ETH address; (3) If address in ADMINS, full access; (4) If document unprotected, anyone reads, authenticated users write; (5) If protected, check explicit grants. Grants support direct user grants, group grants, and inherited grants (drive -> folder -> document). Permission levels: READ (view), WRITE (edit, includes READ), ADMIN (manage permissions, includes WRITE). Configured via env vars (AUTH_ENABLED, ADMINS, DEFAULT_PROTECTION, DOCUMENT_PERMISSIONS_ENABLED) or `powerhouse.config.json`. Env vars override config file values.",
